🚀 Start your 2026 strong with a career-defining experience at P&G!

Applications are now open for our January 2026 Internship Program — your chance to learn, lead, and make an impact from day one. ✨

You may apply to following functions through the links below:
Sales - https://bit.ly/Jan2026SLSIntern
Finance & Accounting - https://bit.ly/Jan2026FAIntern
Product Supply - https://bit.ly/Jan2026PSIntern
Information Technology - https://bit.ly/Jan2026ITIntern
Brand Management - https://bit.ly/Jan2026BRMIntern 

📍 Open to penultimate and graduating students
🗓️ Internship Start Date: January 2026
📩 Deadline: September 30, 2025
#PGInternship #PGCareers #JanuaryInternship
